Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Gapan National High School in the Municipality of Gapan, Province of Nueva Ecija, to Juan R. Liwag Memorial High School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 858
An Act Changing the Name of the Gapan National High School in the Municipality of Gapan, Province of Nueva Ecija, to Juan R. Liwag Memorial High School
Section 1. The name of the Gapan National High School in the Municipality of Gapan, Province of Nueva Ecija, is changed to Juan R. Liwag Memorial High School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
